      "text": [
        "92 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «اِغْسِلْ يَدَكَ مِنَ اَلنَّوْمِ مَرَّةً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.92 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"When you wake up from your sleep, wash your hands once”."
